      • setBinding

        public static BindingExpression setBinding(DependencyObject target,
                           DependencyProperty dp,
                           Binding binding)
        Attach a BindingExpression to a property. A new BindingExpression is created from the given description, and attached to the given property of the given object. This method is the way to attach a Binding to an arbitrary DependencyObject that may not expose its own SetBinding method.
        Parameters:
        target - object on which to attach the Binding
        dp - property to which to attach the Binding
        binding - description of the Binding
        Returns:
        BindingExpression
